title: January 16 Collapsed and Damaged Buildings Merged
name: January 16 Collapsed and Damaged Buildings Merged
description:
This dataset merges and cleans up the following two datasets on January 16th
 
Collapsed Buildings in Haiti metadata 
This data was pulled from OpenStreetMap through GeoFrabrik's update site. The data was originally polygon outlines, but these proved to be difficult to see on many maps. So, I converted them to points so more noticeable icons could be attached to the locations. The collapsed buildings were identified using imagery donated by GeoEye Inc.

 
Haiti Building Damage from OSM (uploaded by ajturner)
Conditions of collapsed buildings in Haiti after the 2010 earthquake. Derived from satellite imagery and marked in OpenStretMap.

Unverified user-generated content. Use only has indication of potential building conditions.
